{"tid":1648012,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"希望可以幫到手足","createTime":"2019-10-12T04:07:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-12T04:07:25.000Z","uid":293340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"1c6e8fca46090aa8ff8805c19eb527ff480c8696","tid":1648012,"uid":293340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T04:07:25.000Z","msg":"大家知唔知Google地圖有一個功能叫做 時間軸？呢個功能可以將你每日到過嘅地方都會有記錄，咁如果有人去發夢嘅時候俾人拉咗，佢嘅朋友就可以上呢個Google地圖嘅 時間軸 睇返佢去過邊度，又或者去嗰邊過個狗屋。前提係你要將你個啊account login 俾一個你信得過嘅人，咁樣可以當遇到被失蹤嘅時候都有啲幫助。<br />\n<br />\n下面有幾條link可以比&hellip;資料作為參考。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.newmobilelife.com/2019/03/05/google-maps-timeline/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newmobilelife.com%2F2019%2F03%2F05%2Fgoogle-maps-timeline%2F&d=Au6C6jYmoXJsWFOyr%2BboKAg0DHywPMniAnH04N%2BeXdM%3D&h=c67d27ff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.newmobilelife.com/2019/03/05/google-maps-timeline/</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com/amp/s/www.pkstep.com/archives/36772\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Famp%2Fs%2Fwww.pkstep.com%2Farchives%2F36772&d=Au6C6jYmoXJsWFOyr%2BboKAg0DHywPMniAnH04N%2BeXdM%3D&h=226047ce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/amp/s/www.pkstep.com/archives/36772</a>"}]}